title: What Model and Houston Native Katie Moore Is Packing for the Super Bowl
text: Here’s What a Rising Model Packs in Her Super Bowl Beauty Kit February 3, 2017 10:10 PM 1 / 8 Photographed by Coco Capitan, *Vogue*, December 2016 Anyone who has ever settled into a Super Bowl stadium knows that game-day beauty goes beyond the flick of Patriots-blue liner or glitter-dusted eyelids in Falcons red. Longevity is key: After all, your look has to take you from tailgate to touchdown, and a few well-chosen essentials can go a long way. Where to start? Just ask model Katie Moore, the Houston native who broke onto the fashion scene last year with her signature fiery red bob. Here, she shares her must-pack products, including Caudalie’s plant-based Beauty Elixir for an instant boost of hydration, Bumble and Bumble’s beloved surf spray for a cool-girl take on Texas texture, and a lip balm to keep the cheers going all night long.
